data.description: Rare opportunity to own one of the larger lots in Christopher Creek! Welcome to paradise! This beautiful and well kept home is completely surrounded by mature trees and lush green landscaping. This 2 bedroom 1.75 bath home offers a huge loft and craft/sewing room. The home has extra insulation to keep it warm in the winters and cool in the summers. There are breathtaking forest views from every window and three patios. Take in the tranquility and panoramic view from your over sized covered patio or enjoy a nice cup of coffee on the quaint balcony off the great room. If you want even better views of the property, enjoy the upstairs deck attached to the loft! The soaring vaulted ceiling and beautiful natural stone fireplace make the great room perfect for entertaining. Christopher Creek close to many hiking trails, creeks, and even lakes for fishing. If you're looking for a place to unwind and relax, this is it! Even the local elk, squirrels, and blue jays agree! You'll often see them on the property enjoying the shade and quiet serenity that this home offers. There is plenty of storage throughout the inside of the home and a spacious workshop for any outdoor projects. There is ample parking on site so bring all your toys!
